reviews.review_text:
Cool Source When i first happened upon this website a few years ago i was confronted with an audience tape of this recording that changed the way i looked at music as a whole this is one of my favorite tapes its cool to hear a different source of something that i genuinely dig. Great fucking dark star totally ripping, cool little feeling groovy jam in the first section well jammed, crazy freekout wah tiger distortion thing from the great Gar brings it to a thundering ending.
the whole show is typical 72 deliciousness but this dark star is very special rite up there with 9/21  or any legendary 73 showings thank god for jerry garcia.
